1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:08,220
 There's a rhythm that most of us fall into, going through the motions of our lives.

2
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:14,540
 Stay busy, stay distracted, stay numb, sleepwalking through life.

3
00:00:14,540 --> 00:00:17,100
 But what if there's more?

4
00:00:17,100 --> 00:00:23,980
 More than just getting by, more than just existing, a life that is fully alive.

5
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:30,220
 We need a holy interruption.

6
00:00:30,220 --> 00:00:35,580
 This Labor Day weekend, thousands of young adults will gather in Dallas, Texas, to sing,

7
00:00:35,580 --> 00:00:40,380
 to listen, to find joy, to seek the presence of God together.

8
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,180
 Hosted by The Porch, we are calling on the name of the Lord to transform our generation,

9
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:52,900
 to awaken our hearts to renewal, to awaken our lives to what truly satisfies.

10
00:00:52,900 --> 00:01:00,380
 Join voices like Kylan Perry, Matt Chandler, Jenny Allen, The Porch Worship, David Platt,

11
00:01:00,380 --> 00:01:06,660
 and Christine King, and step into a space where faith becomes real, where truth cuts

12
00:01:06,660 --> 00:01:11,940
 through the noise, and where you encounter God in a way that changes everything.

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:12,980
 This is your wake-up call.

